# Hugging Face Spaces require binary artifacts to be stored via Git LFS.
# The deploy branch (see deploy-hf.sh) force-adds these data files; LFS keeps the
# push acceptable. On GitHub these patterns are gitignored, so this is a no-op there.
*.parquet filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.db filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
